Almost Tight Approximation Hardness for Single-Source Directed k-Edge-Connectivity 单源定向 k 边连接的近乎严格的近似硬度 In the $k$-connected directed Steiner tree problem ($k$-DST), we are given an $n$-vertex directed graph $G=(V,E)$ with edge costs, a connectivity requirement $k$, a root $r\in V$ and a set of terminals $T\subseteq V$. The goal is to find a minimum-cost subgraph $H\subseteq G$ that has $k$ internally disjoint paths from the root vertex $r$ to every terminal $t\in T$. In this paper, we show the approximation hardness of $k$-DST for various parameters, which thus close some long-standing open problems. - $Ω\left(|T|/\log |T|ight)$-approximation hardness, which holds under the standard assumption $\mathrm{NP}
eq \mathrm{ZPP}$. The inapproximability ratio is tightened to $Ω\left(|T|ight)$ under the Strongish Planted Clique Hypothesis [Manurangsi, Rubinstein and Schramm, ITCS 2021]. The latter hardness result matches the approximation ratio of $|T|$ obtained by a trivial approximation algorithm, thus closing the long-standing open problem. - $Ω\left(\sqrt{2}^k / kight)$-approximation hardness for the general case of $k$-DST under the assumption $\mathrm{NP}
eq\mathrm{ZPP}$. This is the first hardness result known for survivable network design problems with an inapproximability ratio exponential in $k$. - $Ω\left((k/L)^{L/4}ight)$-approximation hardness for $k$-DST on $L$-layered graphs for $L\le O\left(\log night)$. This almost matches the approximation ratio of $O(k^{L-1}\cdot L \cdot \log |T|)$ achieving in $O\left(n^Light)$-time due to Laekhanukit [ICALP`16]. 在 $k$ 连接的有向 Steiner 树问题 ($k$-DST) 中，我们给出一个 $n$ 顶点有向图 $G=(V,E)$，其边成本、连通性要求 $k$、根 $r\in V$ 和一组终端 $T\subseteq V$。目标是找到一个最小成本子图 $H\subseteq G$，它具有从根顶点 $r$ 到每个终端 $t\in T$ 的 $k$ 内部不相交路径。在本文中，我们展示了各种参数的 $k$-DST 的近似硬度，从而解决了一些长期存在的开放性问题。 - $Ω\left(|T|/\log |T|ight)$-近似硬度，在标准假设 $\mathrm{NP}
eq \mathrm{ZPP}$ 下成立。在强植集团假设下，不可逼近率被收紧至 $Ω\left(|T|ight)$ [Manurangsi, Rubinstein 和 Schramm, ITCS 2021]。后者的硬度结果与通过简单近似算法获得的 $|T|$ 的近似比率相匹配，从而解决了长期存在的开放问题。 - $Ω\left(\sqrt{2}^k / kight)$-假设 $\mathrm{NP}
eq\mathrm{ZPP}$ 下 $k$-DST 一般情况的近似硬度。这是第一个已知的可生存网络设计问题的硬度结果，其不可逼近率指数以 $k$ 为单位。 - $Ω\left((k/L)^{L/4}ight)$-$k$ 的近似硬度 - $L\le O\left(\log night)$ 的 $L$ 分层图上的 DST。这几乎与 Laekhanukit [ICALP`16] 在 $O\left(n^Light)$ 时间内实现的 $O(k^{L-1}\cdot L \cdot \log |T|)$ 的近似比率相匹配。 本文研究单源有向k边连通性问题的近似硬度，证明了在不同参数下的近似算法下界，解决了长期未决的开放问题。 Chao Liao,Qingyun Chen,Bundit Laekhanukit,Yuhao Zhang cs.DS,cs.CC,math.OC
